<p>Start by comparing complete quotes. A complete quote should separate equipment, installation, monthly plan, mounting accessories, networking extras, power backup, taxes, transport, and support. If two sellers give different prices, compare what is included before assuming one is cheaper. The lower quote may exclude items you will still need.</p>

